room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Lost Meatball" by Great Room Escape in Columbus
room_description: Legend has it that Da Vinci choked to death while eating the legendary meatball. You will be transported back in time to one hour before Da Vinci’s “Last Supper” where you must outwit Da Vinci and save his life while helping the chef Lorenzo get on the path to have a 5-star restaurant!
